<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #0A1628; color: #fff; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; color: #FFD700; }
    .body { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
    .warning { color: #dc2626; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #999; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Basketball Competition</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p class="warning">Registration Update</p>
      <p>Dear <strong>{{teamName}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>Unfortunately, your payment for the Basketball Competition could not be verified.</p>
      <p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}</p>
      <p>Please contact the organizers if you believe this is an error, or re-submit your registration with valid proof of payment.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br/>Basketball Competition Organizers</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Basketball Competition. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
